### NEAR, Sui, and Aptos Staking Yields Comparison (November 2025)

Staking yields on these Layer 1 protocols vary based on network participation, inflation, and validator performance. NEAR offers the highest potential (up to 22% via locked staking), driven by high rewards for long-term locks, while Sui and Aptos prioritize stability with lower but consistent 3-7% APYs. Data reflects current estimates; actual yields fluctuate with epochs and demand. All are delegated staking with low entry barriers (no fixed minimum like ETH).

